data.name: introTxt.Text
data.value: 120 days...... Thats how long I have been stuck in this cursed dark room. 120 days since I have seen another person, heard another voice or been outside. I have tried every way possible of breaking out but to no avail. The door is a solid slab of steel, there's no windows, the ventilation ducts are too small for me to fit in and the walls are made of solid concrete. There is running water in a sink in the room and there was a huge supply of non perishable emergency food but I am running low. I don't know if I was kidnapped and forgotten about, if this is some sort of sick torture game being ran by a psychopath or someone I wronged in the past taking revenge. But one thing is for certain, if I don't get out of here soon I will go insane...... I think I am going to take a nap now.
